## Context
Author's own reread of the near-final manuscript (2026-07-17, ahead of resubmission)
flagged that the CTF loan's concessionality is evaluated against a single OECD/DAC
reference rate, which sits awkwardly for a multilateral (World Bank) blend rather than
bilateral aid. Proposed evaluating it as a range against two more concrete counterfactuals.

